          <p class="hero-tag">The Buckz Resells promise</p>
          <h2 class="hero-card-title">Real items, real prices.</h2>
          <p class="hero-card-text">
            Buckz Resells is built for people who actually wear what they buy. We source clean pairs and pieces, check
            everything by hand, and keep prices as close to steals as possible.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-chip-row">
            <span class="hero-chip">Curated inventory</span>
            <span class="hero-chip">Secure Ecwid checkout</span>
            <span class="hero-chip">DM-friendly support</span>
